OL,3,GOPINIONCFreeview switch-off: a history
OL,4,Clesson
OL,5,
OL,6,FIt was a complicated change for
OL,7,Fbusinesses to handle. A number of adult
OL,8,Feducation films were shown on BBC TV in
OL,9,Fthe weeks beforehand, one of which was
OL,10,Fentitled Training for D Day.
OL,12,FIt was shown at 9am each morning in the
OL,13,Fweek before decimalisation.
OL,15,FBut from a consumer point of view, you
OL,16,Fmight imagine it was a straightforward
OL,17,Fchange. A complex system was being
OL,18,Freplaced by one which was logical and
OL,19,Fstraightforward.
OL,23,EPub: 15-Feb-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
