OL,3,GOPINIONCFreeview switch-off: a history
OL,4,Clesson
OL,5,
OL,6,FIn fact some older and vulnerable
OL,7,Fpeople found the change difficult. Some
OL,8,Fwere anxious or tried to resist.
OL,10,FA lengthy public information film was
OL,11,Fmade with them in mind.
OL,13,FIt was called Granny Gets the Point and
OL,14,Fwas shown regularly as a scheduled
OL,15,Fprogramme in many ITV regions. You can
OL,16,Fsee it on YouTube.
OL,18,FThere were intense preparations for
OL,19,Fdecimalisation over several years.
OL,23,EPub: 15-Feb-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
