OL,3,GOPINIONCFreeview switch-off: a history
OL,4,Clesson
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe numbers listening to Radio 4 on
OL,7,Flong wave are not publicised but are
OL,8,Fthought to be tiny. If Five Live came
OL,9,Foff MW, I am sure most of its listeners
OL,10,Fwould easily find it on digital radio.
OL,12,FYet concern for a small minority is
OL,13,Fundoubtedly the main reason why the end
OL,14,Fof AM radio has been such a slow,
OL,15,Fcareful process.
OL,17,FSo it is time for the government to
OL,18,Fmake the prerequisites for switching
OL,19,Foff public services on Freeview clear.
OL,23,EPub: 15-Feb-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
