OL,3,GOPINIONCFreeview switch-off: a history
OL,4,Clesson
OL,5,
OL,6,FDecimalisation went far more smoothly
OL,7,Fthan some feared in 1971. The trick was
OL,8,Fa gradualist approach to ensure the
OL,9,Fvast bulk of people were more than
OL,10,Fready combined with a lot of help for
OL,11,Fthose who really needed it.
OL,13,FAnyone contemplating the end of
OL,14,FFreeview should consider this lesson.
